SUMMARY
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

This commit delivers three interconnected enhancements:

1. **Deterministic NeuroFlow**: Seeded weight initialization enables reproducible
   ML experiments essential for scientific rigor. Same seed → same weights → same
   evolutionary outcomes.

2. **Comprehensive Testing**: Environment override validation and brain registration
   tests provide confidence in configuration system correctness. Determinism tests
   verify reproducibility end-to-end.

3. **Interactive Visualization**: Camera controls (pan/zoom) and canvas renderer
   provide real-time visual feedback on evolutionary dynamics. Users can explore
   large worlds and zoom into individual agent interactions.

Together, these features establish production-ready infrastructure for evolutionary
experiments with NeuroFlow brains, full testability, and interactive observation.

